text: INSP is an American digital cable television network. It features primarily westerns. It is headquartered in Indian Land, South Carolina - a suburb of Charlotte, North Carolina. It was originally a non-profit ministry focused network. It was relaunched as a socially conservative, commercial-supported family entertainment network in 2010. It was launched in 1978.
